00:33:51,842 --> 00:33:54,378
- Are you babysitting?
- No.

624
00:33:55,580 --> 00:33:57,947
- Hello.
- Hello.

625
00:33:57,982 --> 00:34:02,618
Roger Sterling, this is Dr.
Emile and Marie Calvet.

626
00:34:02,653 --> 00:34:04,654
You ladies look ravishing.

