742
00:40:30,421 --> 00:40:33,990
<i>From the Sterling Cooper Draper
Pryce advertising firm...</i>

743
00:40:34,024 --> 00:40:36,192
- Oh, your daddy's next.
- <i>Mr. Donald Draper.</i>

744
00:40:38,729 --> 00:40:41,029
Thank you.

